MechWarrior 4: Vengeance is a computer game developed by FASA Interactive and published by Microsoft
It was released on November 22, 2000
This game is the fourth game in MechWarrior series
It takes place in BattleTech universe where the pinnacle of all war machines are huge, heavily armed robots called BattleMechs
The player pilots one of these "'Mechs" and uses variety of available weapons (autocannons, lasers, missiles, and more) to battle enemy 'Mechs, tanks and other vehicles
An expansion pack, MechWarrior 4: Black Knight, was released in 2001, and a subsequent stand-alone expansion, MechWarrior 4: Mercenaries, was released on November 7, 2002.